						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the temple of Chennakēśava.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1319, Īśvara, Pushya, śu. 7, Thursday, Uttarāyaṇa Saṅkrānti, corresponding to 1398 A.D., January 25.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the gift of land in the village of Toṇḍapi to the god Kēśavadēva of Bikkibaṇḍa by Daṇḍi Peddi of Śrīvatsa-gōtra.</p>						

